// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0111 — Mass File Rename (blacksuit)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 17eece96-ee9c-5536-9c84-b916930df541

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
